### ========================================
### POSTS TESTS
### ========================================
@host = {{$dotenv HOST}}
@access_token = {{$dotenv ACCESS_TOKEN}}

### 1. Get Single Post
GET {{host}}/post/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 2. Get Feed
GET {{host}}/feed
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 3. Trending (today)
GET {{host}}/trending?timeframe=today
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 4. Trending (week)
GET {{host}}/trending?timeframe=week
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 5. Trending (month)
GET {{host}}/trending?timeframe=month
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 6. Upload Meme
POST {{host}}/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="meme_image"; filename="meme.jpeg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./meme.jpeg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="caption"

Check out this meme!
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

funny
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="visibility"

public
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="tags"

funny
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="tags"

meme
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 7. Delete Post
DELETE {{host}}/delete_post/2
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}